	)
	(text_box "To configure: (Pg.8)\nSYNC (Tied to Clock Phase 2) DONE\nRT (Set default frequency to 400khz) DONE\nEN/UV threshold (~24v = UV, due to Li-ion discharge)(Pg. 15) DONE\nPGND (Tie to GND) DONE\nSW (Tie to inductor and setup the boost capacitor) DONE\nBST (add 0.1uF bypass cap) DONE\nINTVCC (add 0.1uF bypass cap) DONE\nBIAS (If Vout is greater than 3.3v tie to vout)\nFB (Set Vout via R1 and R2 using FB Setup Pg.12) DONE\nTR/SS (Select a soft start time) ~1s -> 2.16uF DONE\nNC (Tie to ground) DONE"
		(exclude_from_sim no)
		(at 14.478 164.846 0)
		(size 61.595 30.48)
