	(text_box "WD_EN_Jetson is held low at the WD side. If the OBC wants to enable the Jetson board, it must hold the enable line high long enough for the Load Switch, Switching Regulator and Watch dog to power up. Once this is done the WD_EN_PERIF will hold the EN pin high until no pet is recieved.\nWhen no pet is recieved, the WD will turn off the whole system, here we need to use the crowbarred circuit to ensure that the watch dog has enough current to re-enable the load switch."
		(exclude_from_sim no)
		(at 65.278 17.018 0)
		(size 26.67 17.78)
		(margins 0.9525 0.9525 0.9525 0.9525)
		(stroke
			(width 0)
			(type solid)
		)
		(fill
